# AVAudioVoiceProcessingOtherAudioDuckingConfiguration.Level.max

**Case**

Applies maximum ducking to other audio.

## Declaration

```swift
case max
```

## Ducking levels

- **AVAudioVoiceProcessingOtherAudioDuckingConfiguration.Level.default**: The default ducking level for typical voice chat.
- **AVAudioVoiceProcessingOtherAudioDuckingConfiguration.Level.mid**: Applies medium ducking to other audio.
- **AVAudioVoiceProcessingOtherAudioDuckingConfiguration.Level.min**: Applies minimum ducking to other audio.
